{"tid":1884600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今年DSE考生真係好慘, 求巴絲幫手","createTime":"2020-02-17T16:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T14:43:41.000Z","uid":296693,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4722ac5ea32c83b8bfdcd1179dfd8c81c1292521","tid":1884600,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">認真， 2019年運動， 2020年武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年中學生簡直<span style=\"color: red;\">無返過學咁樣</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己以前冇錢補習，所以完全明白而家啲學生有幾辛苦<br />\n<br />\n雖然話就話可以WhatsApp TG問朋友，但係始終係差啲<br />\n<br />\n我而家讀緊大學，成日會去圖書館自修室溫書，發覺同陌生人溫書其實有好多好處。雖然大家未必係知己，但係只要溫嘅topic差唔多，其實係學業上有好多好處。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以我都我用自己渺小嘅力量，整咗呢個網站俾大家，目的係比全港咁多位學生一齊幫大家共渡呢個難關。<br />\n</span><br />\n講真，我自己讀緊書都好忙，所以喺呢個網站度花費嘅時間同精力都有限。但係若果大家真係覺得有用，又可以比意見我點樣改善，我會盡力嘗試幫大家建立一個完美嘅平台。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.brightstars-hk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brightstars-hk.com&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbD%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=a88e5ec9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.brightstars-hk.com</a><br />\n入邊仲有大量 past paper, question bank, notes, 中學 mock etc<br />\n<br />\n比 WhatsApp / telegram / forum 好嘅原因:<br />\n1. 集合全港手足，冇群組人數限制<br />\n2. 每一個答案，全世界都可以見到<br />\n3. 問完問題可以答，答完問題可以問，無分你我，識答嘅就幫<br />\n4. 集合海量文件，網站註冊係英國，唔會俾人 take down <br />\n5. 下載 Wix App 就可以令手機收到通知<br />\n<br />\n🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩各位義教去幫手答問題<br />\n麻煩各位教師 upload 教學資源<br />\n麻煩各位學生盡情問問題同埋比意見</span></span>"},{"pid":"4c2c1eaebf3f00b4c679ab7ba4cbd60e7cd7bbef","tid":1884600,"uid":229020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T01:36:44.000Z","msg":"2020DSER 幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803adfb84fee49d895e24a92350d0b1960494210","tid":1884600,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T02:32:12.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推!!!!!"},{"pid":"a8e244485c04431c492256ba32ddad621aea69eb","tid":1884600,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:25:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e6c67afd36df54bb7a80f372c0b0696c766cfbc","tid":1884600,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:14:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a70d46b32e9d5468e7234553547a47d75fcbe79e","tid":1884600,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T09:46:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f32bacfc2a3b8e0742c49625c2c2533690d8a8e1","tid":1884600,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:15:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2382c9cf4799f0397edc1d6fe3f2919d681517a4","tid":1884600,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:58:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80a49bf26c2e93bd1f6f7967019df3efdace25ba","tid":1884600,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:32:17.000Z","msg":"唔熟中學課程 但幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b44e6938c641a5826943a3bc26f8b4d65c9aa1","tid":1884600,"uid":318720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:35:05.000Z","msg":"空氣推"},{"pid":"55c7c920abf8142480528be8e47cb99eeeb0ab24","tid":1884600,"uid":216628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:53:37.000Z","msg":"推～"},{"pid":"0fdebc3f972074f9c2be2ec910d1c18246a315d0","tid":1884600,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:31:30.000Z","msg":"無力推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed28269b0256d8bf5e7461173c41d3662002cee","tid":1884600,"uid":296693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:05:43.000Z","msg":"多謝大家幫手推!"},{"pid":"ed20bef6608c8cc399f8acc848940a25af95abb7","tid":188460